<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="icon" href="images/store-logo.png"> 
    <title>Urban row</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <style>
        /* Global styles */
        :root {
            --primary-color: #088178;
            --secondary-color: #2c3e50;
            --light-gray: #f8f9fa;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        /* Banner styles */
        .about-banner {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(17, 18, 18, 0.8), rgba(8, 129, 120, 0.7)),
                url('/api/placeholder/1200/300') center/cover;
            padding: 80px 0;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            border-radius: 12px;
        }

        .banner-content {
            text-align: center;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .banner-content h1 {
            font-size: 42px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .banner-content p {
            font-size: 18px;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        /* Breadcrumb styles */
        .breadcrumb {
            margin: 0 0 20px 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .breadcrumb a {
            color: rgba(17, 15, 15, 0.968);
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .breadcrumb span {
            margin: 0 10px;
            color: #666;
        }

        /* Card styles */
        .about-card {
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            padding: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            border-top: 4px solid #088178;
        }

        .about-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
        }

        /* Section header styles */
        .section-header {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .section-header::after {
            content: '';
            display: block;
            width: 60px;
            height: 3px;
            background-color: #088178;
            margin-top: 8px;
        }

        /* Team member styles */
        .team-member {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .team-img {
            width: 180px;
            height: 180px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border: 5px solid #f8f9fa;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .team-img:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            border-color: #088178;
        }

        .team-member h4 {
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .team-member .text-muted {
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        /* Values icon styles */
        .values-icon {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #088178;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .values-icon:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }

        /* CTA Button */
        .btn-cta {
            background-color: #088178;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 2px solid #088178;
        }

        .btn-cta:hover {
            background-color: transparent;
            color: #088178;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(8, 129, 120, 0.15);
        }

        /* Responsive styles */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .about-banner {
                padding: 50px 0;
            }

            .banner-content h1 {
                font-size: 32px;
            }

            .banner-content p {
                font-size: 16px;
                padding: 0 20px;
            }

            .about-card {
                padding: 25px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <%-include("../../views/partials/user/header")%>


    <div class="container my-4">
        <!-- Breadcrumb -->
        <div class="breadcrumb">
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <span>/</span>
            <a href="/about">About Us</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Hero Banner -->
        <div class="about-banner">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="banner-content">
                    <h1>Our Story</h1>
                    <p>Crafting exceptional shopping experiences since 2024</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <!-- Who We Are Section -->
            <div class="col-12">
                <div class="about-card">
                    <div class="section-header">
                        <h2>Who We Are</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row align-items-center">
                        <div class="col-lg-6">
                            <p>Welcome to <strong>URBAN ROW</strong>, where quality meets convenience. We started as a small store in Calicut and have grown into a trusted online destination for men's fashion and lifestyle products.</p>
                            <p>Our journey began in 2024 when our founder, Midlaj Kasim, recognized the need for a shopping platform that combines high-quality products with exceptional customer service. What started as a passion project has evolved into a thriving e-commerce business serving customers nationwide.</p>
                            <p>At <strong>URBAN ROW</strong>, we believe shopping should be enjoyable, easy, and personalized. We handpick every item in our collection to ensure they meet our standards for quality, style, and value.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-6">
                            <img src="images/shopImage.png" alt="Our store" class="img-fluid rounded shadow">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Our Mission Section -->
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="about-card h-100">
                    <div class="section-header">
                        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                    </div>
                    <p>Our mission is to provide customers with a seamless shopping experience that combines high-quality products, competitive prices, and exceptional service.</p>
                    <p>We strive to:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li class="mb-2">Curate collections that inspire and delight</li>
                        <li class="mb-2">Build lasting relationships with our customers</li>
                        <li class="mb-2">Support ethical manufacturing practices</li>
                        <li class="mb-2">Minimize our environmental footprint</li>
                        <li>Create a positive impact in the communities we serve</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Our Vision Section -->
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="about-card h-100">
                    <div class="section-header">
                        <h2>Our Vision</h2>
                    </div>
                    <p>We envision a world where online shopping is not just a transaction but an experience that adds value to people's lives. We aim to be the preferred destination for customers seeking quality products and personalized service.</p>
                    <p>Looking ahead, we plan to expand our product range, enhance our technological capabilities, and strengthen our commitment to sustainability. Our goal is to set new standards in e-commerce by combining innovation with a deep understanding of customer needs.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Our Values Section -->
            <div class="col-12">
                <div class="about-card">
                    <div class="section-header">
                        <h2>Our Values</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row text-center">
                        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                            <div class="values-icon">
                                <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                            </div>
                            <h4>Quality</h4>
                            <p>We never compromise on the quality of our products and services. Every item in our collection undergoes rigorous quality checks to ensure customer satisfaction.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                            <div class="values-icon">
                                <i class="bi bi-people-fill"></i>
                            </div>
                            <h4>Customer First</h4>
                            <p>Our customers are at the heart of everything we do. We continuously listen and adapt to meet their evolving needs and preferences.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                            <div class="values-icon">
                                <i class="bi bi-recycle"></i>
                            </div>
                            <h4>Sustainability</h4>
                            <p>We are committed to reducing our environmental impact through sustainable practices in sourcing, packaging, and operations.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Our Team -->
            <div class="col-12">
                <div class="about-card">
                    <div class="section-header">
                        <h2>Meet Our Team</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6">
                            <div class="team-member">
                                <img src="images/ceoImage.jpeg" alt="Muhammed Anees P P" class="team-img">
                                <h4>Midlaj Kasim</h4>
                                <p class="text-muted">Founder & CEO</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6">
                            <div class="team-member">
                                <img src="images/creator.png" alt="Aseem Roshan" class="team-img">
                                <h4>Abhiram</h4>
                                <p class="text-muted">Operations Director</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6">
                            <div class="team-member">
                                <img src="images/creator2.png" alt="Midlaj Kasim" class="team-img">
                                <h4>Mark John</h4>
                                <p class="text-muted">Creative Director</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6">
                            <div class="team-member">
                                <img src="images/creator3.png" alt="Muhammed Ashique" class="team-img">
                                <h4>Muhammed Ashique</h4>
                                <p class="text-muted">Tech Lead</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Call to Action -->
            <div class="col-12">
                <div class="about-card text-center">
                    <h3>Ready to Experience the URBAN ROW Difference?</h3>
                    <p class="mb-4">Join thousands of satisfied customers and discover why we're a trusted name in online shopping.</p>
                    <a href="/shop" class="btn btn-cta">Shop Now</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%-include("../../views/partials/user/footer")%>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>